 qeynos hills i had 2  young players about lvl 7 or so asking me for cash. i tried to pretend to be afk but they are not fooled so easily. i agreed to give them some money but id have to go to the bank first. so me and my wiz friend went to the bank and each got 20pp for each of the two newbies sitting there. 20pp in copper that is. we came back (disguised as skeletons using ammy, i was on my druid at the time). we gave the newbies their copper and sat to watch the show.<br>
<br>
noob01: hey i cant move is my game messed up<br>
<br>
noob02: i cannot move either hey whats going on here<br>
<br>
me: wow all that cash weighs so much i guess it encumbered you! im so sorry want me to take it back?<br>
<br>
bothnoobs: nooooooo!<br>
<br>
noob01: can you cast a spell on me for strength or like to run fast or something?<br>
<br>
me: cant you see we are necros? sorry we have none of those kinds of spells sire.<br>
<br>
they finally got smart and thought of a plan where one person would hold most of the cash and the other would run to the bank and come back for more etc etc. until it was all in the bank. but of course we didnt want either of them to get scammed so we had to warn them of potential trickery here.<br>
<br>
noob02: hey one of us can run to the bank with a little of the money and keep coming back until its all transfered.<br>
<br>
noob01: that sounds ok, ill do it if you want.<br>
<br>
me: wow good idea. but noob01 sounds a little anxious to get his hands on all that money - are you sure you trust him to give him all of your money?<br>
<br>
noob02: ....<br>
<br>
they stood there for like 10 minutes just doing nothing. gnolls were starting to wander close. i left like five minutes later so i have no idea what happened to these guys. it was pretty funny though.<br>
